data.description: Welcome to this waterfront home on the scenic Calcasieu River! This property offers 100 feet of prime riverfront frontage, featuring a sturdy bulkhead and a spacious 24'x22' dock complete with a boat slip rated for a substantial 6,000 lbs. Whether you're a boating enthusiast or love to soak in the tranquil river views, this property offers an idyllic setting. The dock is a true waterfront haven with water, electricity, and a security light. Spend lazy afternoons casting a line, embark on a sunset cruise, or bask in the serenity of riverfront living. You'll be greeted by a large front porch, providing the perfect spot to enjoy morning coffee or sunsets over the river. Inside, the living room boasts vaulted ceilings, creating an airy and spacious ambiance. The open-concept design connects the living area to a generously sized kitchen and an expansive laundry room with a convenient pantry. For those who love outdoor entertaining, the screened-in patio under the home transforms into an ideal space for an outdoor kitchen or a lively gathering with friends and family. Ample parking is available, accommodating multiple vehicles and an RV, making this property perfect for hosting gatherings and events. The residence features four bedrooms and three bathrooms, with a unique attached apartment or mother-in-law suite. This self-contained space includes one of the four bedrooms and one of the three bathrooms, offering flexibility for guests, extended family, or even as a potential rental opportunity. The total square footage includes the mother-in-law's apartment, and the roof is only three years old. With its stunning riverfront views, convenient amenities, and versatile living spaces, this Calcasieu River home is a rare find that seamlessly blends comfort, functionality, and the allure of waterfront living. Take advantage of the opportunity to make this your dream home on the Calcasieu River! All measurements +/- buyer to verify.
